ollapsed}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Imeri, Butrint}}\n[[Category:1996 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from L\u00f6rrach]]\n[[Category:Albanian musicians]]\n[[Category:Albanian pop singers]]\n[[Category:Albanian rhythm and blues singers]]\n[[Category:Albanian male singers]] \n[[Category:Albanian-language singers]] \n[[Category:21st-century Albanian singers]]\n[[Category:21st-century male singers]]\n[[Category:Kosovo Albanians]] \n[[Category:Kosovan people of Albanian descent]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=February 2019}} \n{{Short description|Kosovo singer}}\n{{Infobox musical artist \n| name             = Butrint Imeri\n| image            =  \n| caption          =  \n| background       = solo_singer\n| birth_name       =  \n| birth_date       = {{Birth date and age|df=yes|1996|07|03}}\n| birth_place      = [[L\u00f6rrach]], Germany\n| origin           =  \n| genre            = {{hlist|[[Contemporary R&B|R&B]]|[[Pop music|Pop]]}}\n| occupation       = {{hlist|Singer|songwriter}} \n| years_active     = 2015\u2013present\n| label            = 96 Management\n| associated_acts  =  \n}}\n \n'''Butrint Imeri''' ({{IPA-sq|bu\u02c8t\u027eint i\u02c8m\u025b\u027ei}}; born 3 July 1996) is a [[Kosovo]]- singer and songwriter.<ref name=\"Biography\">{{cite web |title=Butrint Imeri\u2013Biografia |url=https://www.teksteshqip.com/butrint |website=teksteshqip.com |accessdate=3 February 2020 |language=Kosovo }}</ref>\n\n== Life and career ==\nButrint Imeri was born on 3 July 1996 into a Kosovo family in the city of [[L\u00f6rrach]], Germany. He commenced his music career in 2015 and debuted with the singles, \"Ki me lyp\", \"Merre zemr\u00ebn tem\" and \"Eja Eja\", with whom he received significant recognition in the [[Kosovo language|Kosovo-speaking]] world.<ref>{{cite web |title=Lansohet klipi i Butrintit me Real dhe Blunt |url=https://telegrafi.com/lansohet-klipi-i-butrintit-me-real-dhe-blunt-video/ |website=telegrafi.com |accessdate=3 February 2020 |language=Kosovo |date=20 April 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Ylli i ri Butrint Imeri thot\u00eb \u201cMerre Zemr\u00ebn tem\u201d |url=https://telegrafi.com/ylli-i-ri-butrint-imeri-thote-merre-zemren-tem-video/ |website=telegrafi.com |accessdate=3 February 2020 |language=Albanian |date=10 July 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Butrint Imeri me nj\u00eb k\u00ebng\u00eb t\u00eb p\u00eblqyeshme |url=https://telegrafi.com/butrint-imeri-nje-kenge-te-pelqyeshme-video/ |website=telegrafi.com |accessdate=3 February 2020 |language=Kosovo |date=12 April 2016}}</ref> He later released four additional singles including \"E jona\" and \"Delicious\", the latter in collaboration with Greek-Albanian singer [[Eleni Foureira]] which peaked at number five in [[Albania]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Vie \u2018E Jona\u2019 nga Butrint Imeri! |url=https://priveshow.tv/vie-e-jona-nga-butrinti/ |website=[[Klan Kosova|prive.tv]] |accessdate=3 February 2020 |language=Kosovo |date=3 July 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Butrint publikon duetin me Eleni Foureira |url=https://www.botasot.info/mediale-vip-showbiz/552898/butrint-publikon-duetin-me-eleni-foureira-video/ |website=[[Bota Sot|botasot.info]] |accessdate=3 February 2020 |language=Albanian |date=17 June 2016}}</ref>\n\n== Artistry ==\n\nImeri's musical work is often defined as [[Contemporary R&B|R&B]] and [[Pop music|Pop]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Butrint Imeri\u2013Bio |url=http://topawards.top-channel.tv/index.php/artist/butrint-imeri/ |website=topawards.top-channel.tv |accessdate=3 February 2020 |language=Albanian}}</ref><ref name=\"Biography\"/> He has cited [[Justin Timberlake]] as his major musical influence and stated that he is a fan of [[Elvana Gjata]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Cil\u00ebn k\u00ebng\u00ebtare shqiptare e ka t\u00eb preferuar Butrinti |url=https://prive.al/cilen-kengetare-shqiptare-e-ka-te-preferuar-butrinti/ |website=prive.al |accessdate=10 February 2020 |language=Albanian |date=20 April 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Butrint Imeri e thot\u00eb hapur: Un\u00eb dhe Elvana Gjata do ishim \u00e7ifti perfekt |url=https://www.dailyxing.com/news/32143/butrint-imeri-says-it-openly-elvana-gjata-and-i-would-be-the-perfect-couple |website=dailyxing.com |accessdate=10 February 2020 |language=Albanian |date=1 January 2020}}</ref>\n\n== Discography ==\n\n=== Singles ===\n\n==== As lead artist ====\n\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:15em;\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:2em;\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"4\" | Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" | Album\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\" | [[The Top List|ALB]]<br/><ref>Note: ''\"The Top List\" are the charts conducted by [[Top Channel]] since December 2015''. For peak positions in Albania:\n*For \"E jona\":{{cite web |publisher=[[Top Channel|Top Music Awards]] |title=The Top List\u201404/09/2016 |url=http://topawards.top-channel.tv/index.php/04092016/ |website=topawards.top-channel.tv |accessdate=3 February 2020 |language=Albanian}}\n*For \"Delicious\":{{cite web |publisher=[[Top Channel|Top Music Awards]] |title=The Top List\u201403/07/2016 |url=http://topawards.top-channel.tv/index.php/03072016/ |website=topawards.top-channel.tv |accessdate=3 February 2020 |language=Albanian}}\n*For \"Ve\u00e7 p\u00ebr mu\":{{cite web |publisher=[[Top Channel|Top Music Awards]] |title=The Top List\u201407/05/2017 |url=http://topawards.top-channel.tv/index.php/07052017/ |website=topawards.top-channel.tv |accessdate=3 February 2020 |language=Albanian}}\n*For \"Mona Lisa\":{{cite web |publisher=[[Top Channel|Top Music Awards]] |title=The Top List\u201402/07/2017 |url=http://topawards.top-channel.tv/index.php/02072017/ |website=topawards.top-channel.tv |accessdate=3 February 2020 |language=Albanian}}\n*For \"Bella\":{{cite web |publisher=[[Top Channel|Top Music Awards]] |title=The Top List\u201402/07/2017 |url=http://topawards.top-channel.tv/index.php/02072017/ |website=topawards.top-channel.tv |accessdate=3 February 2020 |language=Albanian}}\n*For \"Xhanem\":{{cite web |publisher=[[Top Channel|Top Music Awards]] |title=The Top List\u201407/01/2018 |url=http://topawards.top-channel.tv/index.php/07-01-2018/ |website=topawards.top-channel.tv |accessdate=3 February 2020 |language=Albanian}}\n*For \"Ma Ch\u00e9rie\":{{cite web |publisher=[[Top Channel|Top Music Awards]] |title=The Top List\u201427/05/2018 |url=http://topawards.top-channel.tv/index.php/27-05-2018/ |website=topawards.top-channel.tv |accessdate=3 February 2020 |language=Albanian}}\n*For \"Alea\":{{cite web |publisher=[[Top Channel|Top Music Awards]] |title=The Top List\u201429/07/2018 |url=http://topawards.top-channel.tv/index.php/29-07-2018/ |website=topawards.top-channel.tv |accessdate=3 February 2020 |language=Albanian}}\n*For \"Kush?\":{{cite web |publisher=[[Top Channel|Top Music Awards]] |title=The Top List\u201411/11/2018 |url=http://topawards.top-channel.tv/index.php/10-11-2018/ |website=topawards.top-channel.tv |accessdate=3 February 2020 |language=Albanian}}\n*For \"Bakllava\":{{cite web |publisher=[[Top Channel|Top Music Awards]] |title=The Top List\u201430/12/2018 |url=http://topawards.top-channel.tv/index.php/30-12-2018/ |website=topawards.top-channel.tv |accessdate=3 February 2020 |language=Albanian}}\n*For \"Hajt Hajt\":{{cite web |publisher=[[Top Channel|Top Music Awards]] |title=The Top List\u201404/08/2019 |url=http://topawards.top-channel.tv/index.php/04-08-2019/ |website=topawards.top-channel.tv |accessdate=3 February 2020 |language=Albanian}}\n*For \"[[Dream Girl (Butrint Imeri and Nimo song)|Dream Girl]]\":{{cite web |publisher=[[Top Channel|Top Music Awards]] |title=The Top List\u201422/09/2019 |url=http://topawards.top-channel.tv/index.php/22-09-2019/ |website=topawards.top-channel.tv |accessdate=3 February 2020 |language=Albanian}}\n*For \"M'ke rrejt\":{{cite web 